import { Router } from 'express'
import { UserController } from '../controllers/user'


const router = new Router()


router.route('/').post(UserController.createUser)
router.route('/login').post(UserController.loginUser)
router.route('/admin').post(UserController.createAdmin)


export default router
export { default as UserController} from './userController'

export { default as UserService} from './User'
export { default as HomeService } from './Home'
export { default as AboutService } from './About'
export {  default as ProjectsService  } from './Projects'
export { default as HomeController } from './homeController'
export { default as AuthMiddleware } from './auth'
export { default as AboutController } from './aboutController'
export { default as ProjectController} from './ProjectController'

import { Router } from 'express'
import { UserController } from '../controllers/user'
import { AuthMiddleware } from '../middlewares'

const router = new Router()


router.route('/').post(UserController.createUser)
router.route('/login').post(UserController.loginUser)
router.route('/admin').post(UserController.createAdmin)
router.route('/user/').get(AuthMiddleware.isAuth,AuthMiddleware.isAdmin,UserController.getUser)

export default router
export { default as UserController} from './userController'
export { default as HomeController } from './homeController'
export { default as AuthMiddleware } from './auth'
export { default as AboutController } from './aboutController'
export { default as ProjectController} from './ProjectController'
export {  default as BlogController } from './BlogController'
